---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Getwebify"
  description="How Getwebify collects, uses, and protects your personal data. GDPR compliant."
>
  <section class="max-w-[760px] mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24">

    <p class="font-body text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-5">Legal</p>

    <h1
      class="font-display leading-tight mb-4"
      style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem); font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144"
    >
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>

    <p class="font-body text-sm text-muted mb-10">Last updated: 12 June 2026</p>

    <div class="font-body text-base leading-relaxed space-y-8 text-ink/80">

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink mb-3" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36">Who we are</h2>
        <p>
          Getwebify ("we", "us") is a web design and development agency registered in England &amp; Wales.
          We are the data controller for personal data collected through this website (<strong>www.getwebify.uk</strong>).
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Contact: <a href="mailto:hello@getwebify.uk" class="text-terracotta hover:underline">hello@getwebify.uk</a>
          &nbsp;·&nbsp; WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/447446508333" class="text-terracotta hover:underline">+447446508333</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink mb-3" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36">What data we collect</h2>
        <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-rule">
              <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-ink">Data</th>
              <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-ink">Source</th>
              <th class="text-left py-2 font-medium text-ink">Legal basis</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-muted">
            <tr class="border-b border-rule/50">
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">Name, email, phone, business name, project details</td>
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">Contact form</td>
              <td class="py-2">Legitimate interests (respond to enquiry)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-rule/50">
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">Email address</td>
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">Newsletter signup</td>
              <td class="py-2">Consent</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-rule/50">
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">Page views, device type, country, referrer</td>
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">Google Analytics (only after consent)</td>
              <td class="py-2">Consent (statistics cookies)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">Cookie consent preferences</td>
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">Cookiebot</td>
              <td class="py-2">Legal obligation (PECR / GDPR Art. 7)</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink mb-3" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36">Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We use Cookiebot to manage cookie consent. Review or change your preferences at any time via the
          <button
            onclick="Cookiebot.renew()"
            class="text-terracotta hover:underline cursor-pointer bg-transparent border-none p-0 font-body text-base"
          >Cookie Settings</button> link.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside text-muted">
          <li><strong class="text-ink">Necessary</strong> — Cookiebot consent record. Cannot be disabled.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-ink">Statistics</strong> — Google Analytics (GA4). Only set with your consent.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">We do not use advertising, social media, or tracking cookies beyond the above.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink mb-3" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36">Third-party processors</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted">
          <li><strong class="text-ink">Google Analytics</strong> — analytics (EU–US Data Privacy Framework). <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-terracotta hover:underline">Privacy policy →</a></li>
          <li><strong class="text-ink">Cookiebot (Cybot A/S)</strong> — consent management, servers in EU. <a href="https://www.cookiebot.com/en/privacy-policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-terracotta hover:underline">Privacy policy →</a></li>
          <li><strong class="text-ink">Resend</strong> — email delivery. <a href="https://resend.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-terracotta hover:underline">Privacy policy →</a></li>
          <li><strong class="text-ink">Cloudflare Turnstile</strong> — bot protection on forms. <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-terracotta hover:underline">Privacy policy →</a></li>
          <li><strong class="text-ink">Sanity.io</strong> — CMS. <a href="https://www.sanity.io/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-terracotta hover:underline">Privacy policy →</a></li>
          <li><strong class="text-ink">Vercel</strong> — website hosting. <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-terracotta hover:underline">Privacy policy →</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink mb-3" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36">How long we keep data</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted list-disc list-inside">
          <li>Contact enquiries — until project complete or deletion requested</li>
          <li>Newsletter subscribers — until you unsubscribe</li>
          <li>Analytics data — 26 months (Google Analytics default)</li>
          <li>Cookie consent records — 12 months (Cookiebot default)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink mb-3" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36">Your rights</h2>
        <p>Under UK GDPR and EU GDPR you have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-muted list-disc list-inside">
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion ("right to be forgotten")</li>
          <li>Object to processing based on legitimate interests</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time (does not affect prior lawful processing)</li>
          <li>Data portability</li>
          <li>Lodge a complaint with the <a href="https://ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-terracotta hover:underline">ICO</a> (UK) or your local supervisory authority (EU)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">
          To exercise any right email <a href="mailto:hello@getwebify.uk" class="text-terracotta hover:underline">hello@getwebify.uk</a>. We respond within 30 days.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink mb-3" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36">International transfers</h2>
        <p>
          Google Analytics transfers data to the United States under Google's participation in the EU–US Data Privacy Framework.
          Resend and Vercel provide Standard Contractual Clauses as a transfer safeguard.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink mb-3" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36">Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this policy from time to time. The "last updated" date at the top reflects any changes.
          Material changes will be notified to newsletter subscribers by email.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
